Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.33,0:05:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0080,,达尔玛普星系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.85,0:22:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0040,,罗斯库月11日14时12分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.85,0:22:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴斯罗依尔号战斗开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.94,0:22:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离主力舰队到达还有50小时
